{"url":"https://twitter.com/aarongreenberg/status/1258584474155053058","author_name":"Aaron Greenberg 🙅🏼‍♂️❎","author_url":"https://twitter.com/aarongreenberg","html":"<blockquote class=\"twitter-tweet\"><p lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\">Had we not said anything &amp; just shown May Inside Xbox show like we did last month, I suspect reactions might have been different. Clearly we set some wrong expectations &amp; that’s on us. We appreciate all the feedback &amp; can assure you we will take it all in &amp; learn as a team. 🙏🏻💚</p>&mdash; Aaron Greenberg 🙅🏼‍♂️❎ (@aarongreenberg) <a href=\"https://twitter.com/aarongreenberg/status/1258584474155053058?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw\">May 8, 2020</a></blockquote>\n<script async src=\"https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js\" charset=\"utf-8\"></script>\n","width":550,"height":null,"type":"rich","cache_age":"3153600000","provider_name":"Twitter","provider_url":"https://twitter.com","version":"1.0"}